<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
. However, Freitag (
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="810">in litt.</emphasis>
) has pointed out that this is a mixed sheet of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1756" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Salsola" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tragus">
