<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Salsola" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="kali">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="810">S. kali</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(right) and Rilke (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="810">Biblioth. Bot.</emphasis>
149: 141. 1999) restricts this choice to the right-hand specimen, and also designates an 
<typeStatus>epitype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
